~ start

Mei: Ah, you're finally here! I was starting to think you got lost on the way to the café.
Boss: Don't be rude, Mei. Welcome. I'm glad you made it.
Mei: Sorry sorry! I'm just excited. We've been waiting for a new helper for weeks!
Boss: Welcome to Zen Matcha. Today will be your first day learning the basics. Pay close attention as the steps in making matcha can be very detailed..
Mei: The boss might seem strict but she really does care. I promise!
Boss: Mei.
Mei: R-right! So first things first — we make matcha from scratch here. No shortcuts.
Boss: Every drink starts with properly measured, sifted matcha. Remember that. Our regulars can definitely tell a difference.
Mei: It sounds like a lot but once you get the hang of it, it's actually really fun!
Boss: Fun is secondary. Precision is everything. Shall we begin?
Mei: Let's gooo!!

=> END